content: I don't know the tradeoffs for the storage format options. If something takes a little more time now, but the compound results will be worth it, then I'm fine with that, alternatively, is something manual to start will have better compounding results, I'm good with that too. We want to steepen the curve as quickly as possible while I'm learning along the way. That's the objective, up to you to figure out and I'll do what you say.
